    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>S.T. Anno ab incarnatione domini millesimo centesimo sestodecimo, duodecimo
                        die ingrediente mense madii inditione nona. <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Priors #Monks #Forests #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancto <rs key="#Monasteries"
                                >monasterio</rs> iusta Larionem in onorem sancti Benedicti
                            consecrato</orgName> cui <persName key="#Priors #Monasteries #Priors"
                            ref="#people/3509">Ubertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Priors">prior</rs> adesse videtur. Ego quidem in Dei nomine
                            <persName key="#Emperor/king" ref="#people/127">Henricus</persName>
                        quartus Dei gratia Romanorum <rs key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs>
                        augustus, dono et offero eidem monasterio ad eius ius et proprietatem
                        scilicet <placeName key="#Forests #Fiscal_property" ref="#places/4193"><rs
                                key="#Forests">silva</rs> una que nominatur de Solamine</placeName>
                        et una partae iusta eam que dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Forests #Fiscal_property" ref="#places/4192">silva de
                            Carpeneta</placeName>. Finesque sunt ei a mane sancti Benedicti, ab
                        aliis lateribus sicut vadit stradam de viutlo, sicut vadunt campi de
                        Sergnano et argenem, sicut vadit regisa que exit de Solame et intrat in
                        petrosam, et intrat in vallem Pudiosam, et intrat in vallem Bertaldi, et
                        intrat in vallem Lameleda, et√¨in risisam de nido aquile, et a risisa in
                        riolum. Ut iam dictum monasterium ab hac die in antea faciant <rs
                            key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">proproprientarii iure</rs>, in usum
                        et sumptum <rs key="#Monks">monachorurn</rs> qui in eadem ecclesia militant,
                        et qui militaturi sunt, usque in perpetuum quicquid voluerit sine omni mea
                        et heredum meorum contradictione. Quisquis in sanctis hac in venerabilibus
                        locis ex suis aliquid contulerit rebus, iuxta auctoris vocem in hoc saeculo
                        centuplum accipiet, et insuper quod melius est vitam possidebit eternam.
                        Ideoque ego Henricus imperator similiter dono et offero <orgName
                            key="#Churches #Offersio/donatio #Landed_possessions #Houses"><rs
                                key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> sancti Benedicti de <placeName
                                key="#Churches #Offersio/donatio #Landed_possessions #Houses"
                                ref="#places/2414">Gonzaga</placeName></orgName>, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">braida una</rs> iuris mei posita in eodem loco
                        Gonziachae, cum <rs key="#Houses">casa</rs> camparii super eam habente et
                        hoc quod tenet ex mea parte. Finesque sunt ei: a mane tenei Milo filius Adam
                        Gunbo, a meridie Petrus Cottus, a sera tenet Rotecherius de Gonzaga, de
                        subto Albricus Cocus; hoc quod in hos fines inventum fuerit in hanc cartula
                        permaneat; ut iam dictae aecclesiae faciant cum superioribus et inferioribus
                        cum finibus et accessionibus suarum manu mea quicquid voluerint proprietarii
                        iure sine omni mea et haeredum meorum contradictione, pro mercaede et
                        remedio animae maeae et <rs key="#Countess">comitissae</rs>
                        <persName key="#Countess" ref="#people/125">Matildis</persName>, et insuper
                        comprehensum est ab omni contradicentae homine defendere. Et si defendere
                        non potuerimus, aut si vobis ex inde aliquid per quodlibet ingenium
                        subtraere quesierimus, tunc in duplum has res ut supra legitur eidem
                        aecclesiae restituere sicut pro tempore fuerint meliorate aut valuerint sub
                        extimatione in consimilibus locis. Actum in loco <placeName
                            ref="#places/2418">Gubernule</placeName> feliciter. SM. Huius <rs
                            key="#Offersio/donatio">cartule offersionis</rs> fuerunt <rs
                            key="#Witness">testes</rs>
                        <persName key="#Witness #Count #Offersio/donatio" ref="#people/4038"
                            >Conradus <rs key="#Count">comes</rs></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Count #Offersio/donatio" ref="#people/4037">Albertus
                            comes de <placeName>Saploneta</placeName></persName>. <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio" ref="#people/3500">Ardoinus de
                            Palude</persName>. <persName key="#Witness #Prevosts #Offersio/donatio"
                                ><name ref="Arnaldus/prepositus Aquensis"/>Arnaldus
                                <placeName>Aquensis</placeName>
                            <rs key="#Prevosts">prepositus</rs></persName>. <persName
                            key="#Witness #Judge #Offersio/donatio" ref="#people/3527">Vuarnerius
                                <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Judge #Offersio/donatio" ref="#people/3539">Ubaldus
                            iudex</persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"
                            ref="#people/2194">Amedeus</persName>. <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio" ref="#people/3517">Oppizo de
                            Gonciaga</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Agricultural_workers #Offersio/donatio"><name
                                ref="Gherardus/massarius">Gerardus</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Agricultural_workers #Offersio/donatio"><name
                                ref="Rodelandus/massarius">Rolandus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Agricultural_workers">massarii</rs>, atque <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Paganus"
                            >Paganus</name></persName>. <persName><name ref="Hugo"
                            >Ugo</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Hludouuicus/de Gubernule"
                                >Lodoicus</name></persName> de Gubernule et plures alii. Ego
                        Wernerius judex affui et subscripsi. Ego Ubaldus judex interfui et
                        subscripsi. S.T. Ego <persName key="#Notary #Writer #Offersio/donatio"><name
                                ref="Dominicus/notarius">Dominicus</name></persName> Sacri palacii
                            <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>
                        <rs key="#Writer">scripsi</rs> et subscribendo complevi ex jussione Henrici
                        jmperatoris. </ab>
                </div>
